CONNECT_ACCOUNT_ANNOUNCEMENT:
Connect OpenAI and AIPRM Accounts

We are excited to announce that you can now connect your OpenAI account with your AIPRM account.

This will allow you to save a favorite prompt to the "Favorites" prompts list and to try more of our premium features before subscribing to a premium AIPRM plan.

If you don't have an AIPRM account yet, you can create one for free. It's really simple, as you see here.
CONNECT_ACCOUNT_TO_USE_FAVORITES:
Connect OpenAI and AIPRM Accounts

To use the "Favorites" prompts list, you must connect your OpenAI account with your AIPRM account. This will allow you to save a favorite prompt to the "Favorites" prompts list.

PREMIUM_EXTENSION_DEPRECATION_ANNOUNCEME:
Switch to AIPRM for ChatGPT

We're streamlining our browser extensions to provide a unified experience for all users. As a result, we're deprecating the AIPRM Premium for ChatGPT extension.

Please uninstall the AIPRM Premium for ChatGPT and install the AIPRM for ChatGPT browser extension here to continue enjoying AIPRM features.

Initially, the AIPRM Premium for ChatGPT extension was launched exclusively for early adopters of our AIPRM Premium Plans. Now that these plans are accessible to all users, we're focusing on the AIPRM for ChatGPT extension, which offers the full range of features.

The AIPRM Premium for ChatGPT browser extension will be removed from the Chrome Web Store on April 28th, 2023.

Important: You will not lose any data or prompts. For AIPRM Premium plan customers, this change will not affect your subscription, and you can continue using the AIPRM Premium features with the AIPRM for ChatGPT browser extension.
